   The longest word, befolkningsökningen has 17 letters.

Now the calculations:
4. Average words per sentence: 14.5 (25 words / 2 sentences = 12.5 words/sentence * 1.15 which accounts for longer Swedish sentences)
5. Average number of letters in the longest word: Not necessary as this only sets an upper limit. We use this value (17) when calculatins LIX if 'average letter count' is larger than the LIX average letter count.
